The paper deals with decidability of verification problems for timed automata extended with unbounded discrete data structures, which involves topics related to logic (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL), data structures (cs.DS), and temporal logic (cs.LT).
